Scope=GraphQL 배치 로더 중 표시 단위가 빠진 항목. Given a training environment reproduced without sensitive values; the focus is the entry with a missing unit, review the areas most likely to fail; 경계 입력을 테스트해줘; propagate the failure path to the caller. Constraints=원문의 고유 명칭은 보존하기; deliverable=prioritized review findings.

